{"tid":1471724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"航空傳媒有事 同路人幫同路人","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:17.000Z","uid":68125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a883e05f34a9b4fd1de33e99e7df5288311ffab5","tid":1471724,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1083324738537093?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1083324738537093%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3VQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=352c5d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1083324738537093?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n由今日兩點起，香港國際機場 (HKG) 客運大樓進行管制措施，以下出入口已被封閉，需要出示有效登機證明或需要合理理由 （接機除外） 方可進場。<br />\n<br />\nT1 Departure Hall<br />\n1號入口(兩邊玻璃門全封)<br />\n2號入口(只封其中一邊玻璃門)<br />\n3號入口(只封其中一邊玻璃門)<br />\n4號入口(兩邊玻璃門全封)<br />\n*入口已貼通知只准離境旅客及機場人員進入<br />\n北面安檢入口暫停使用<br />\n<br />\nT1 Arrival Hall<br />\n所有通往巴士站隧道<br />\n<br />\nT2 3樓<br />\n專車候車處<br />\n<br />\n機鐵<br />\n往博覽館方向月台近Hall A<br />\n往博覽館方向月台近Hall B<br />\n往市區方向月台正門<br />\n<br />\n6樓<br />\n停車場通道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同時，由於小編已經不能進入客運大樓拍攝航空照片，專頁營運大受打擊。<br />\n<br />\n可以的，請支持一下我們營運共渡時艱<br />\n想請小編食飯的話，可以PayPal支持</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/KSAviation1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.me%2FKSAviation1&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3VQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=8c3792e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.paypal.me/KSAviation1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">之前人地篤爆中國民航局放氧氣同篤爆機管局假取消，會唔會幫佢手？</span>"},{"pid":"d1f86d1c28eb2691a476140fc6ffa06e569dc3d6","tid":1471724,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8yc